Hi friend, please follow these steps for authorization:
1. Tap "Allow";
2. Make sure the directory title is SD card. If not, tap menu button and switch to SD card;
3. Tap "Select";

Hello. Repeat play is supported:
1. Tap playlist button on bottom right of playback screen;
2. Then you can find play mode on top right of  playlist window;
3. Switch to "Repeat current".
Please let us know if the problem is solved or not. Thanks.
